Amin's Last Chance

March, 1979

The forces of Uganda supported by airlifted reinforcements from Libya tries to delay the advance of Tanzanian and the rebels of Uganda towards Kampala. 

Conditions of victory: 

- To retain until end 4 hexes for BV 
- To retain until end 3 hexes for V 
- To retain until end 2 hexes for TV 

The headquarters of Ugandan president Idi Amin must survive.

